OL,3,CNicholas Rossi: Extradited fugitive
OL,4,Cfound guilty of rape in US court
OL,6,FFugitive Nicholas Rossi, accused of
OL,7,Ffaking his death and fleeing the
OL,8,FUnited States for Scotland, has been
OL,9,Ffound guilty of rape charges.
OL,11,FA jury in the US state of Utah found
OL,12,FRossi guilty of raping a former
OL,13,Fgirlfriend in 2008, following a three-
OL,14,Fday trial.
OL,16,FRossi made headlines after being
OL,17,Farrested in 2021 on the Covid ward of
OL,18,Fa Glasgow hospital.
