OL,3,CNicholas Rossi: Extradited fugitive
OL,4,Cfound guilty of rape in US court
OL,6,FHe consistently argued that his arrest
OL,7,Fwas a case of mistaken identity,
OL,8,Fclaiming he was an Irish orphan named
OL,9,FArthur Knight, who had never been to
OL,10,Fthe US.
OL,12,FA court ruled in November 2022 that he
OL,13,Fwas Nicholas Rossi, and he was
OL,14,Fextradited to the US.
OL,16,FHe will be sentenced in October for
OL,17,Fthis case, and could face between five
OL,18,Fyears and life in prison.
OL,20,FHe is set to stand trial in September
OL,21,Ffor another rape charge.
