OL,3,CNicholas Rossi: Extradited fugitive
OL,4,Cfound guilty of rape in US court
OL,6,FThroughout the trial in Salt Lake
OL,7,FCounty, prosecutors painted a picture
OL,8,Fof an intelligent man who used his
OL,9,Fcharm to take advantage of a
OL,10,Fvulnerable young woman.
OL,12,FThe victim, who was not named, was
OL,13,Fliving with her parents and recovering
OL,14,Ffrom a traumatic brain injury when she
OL,15,Fmet Rossi, after she responded to a
OL,16,Fpersonal ad on Craigslist.
OL,18,FThey began dating and were engaged
OL,19,Fwithin roughly two weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
