OL,6,FShe described being asked to pay for
OL,7,Ftheir dates and Rossi's car repairs.
OL,8,FHe also asked her to lend him $1,000
OL,9,Fso he wouldn't be evicted and to take
OL,10,Fon debt to buy their engagement rings.
