OL,6,FShe didn't go to the police at the
OL,7,Ftime, saying dismissive comments from
OL,8,Fher parents convinced her not to. She
OL,9,Fcame forward a decade later after she
OL,10,Fsaw Rossi on the news, and learned he
OL,11,Fwas accused of another rape from the
OL,12,Fsame year.
OL,14,FRossi's lawyers claimed the accuser
OL,15,Fbuilt up years of resentment after she
OL,16,Fwas made to foot the bill for
OL,17,Feverything during the monthlong
OL,18,Frelationship, and that her accusation
OL,19,Fwas an act of revenge after she saw he
OL,20,Fwas getting media attention.
