OL,6,FRossi grew up in foster homes in Rhode
OL,7,FIsland and had returned there before
OL,8,Fallegedly faking his death.
OL,10,FHe was previously wanted in the state
OL,11,Ffor failing to register as a sex
OL,12,Foffender. The FBI says he also faces
OL,13,Ffraud charges in Ohio, where he was
OL,14,Fconvicted of sex-related charges in
OL,15,F2008.
OL,17,FIn Utah, first-degree felony rape
OL,18,Fcarries a punishment of five years to
OL,19,Flife in prison, said Salt Lake County
OL,20,FDistrict Attorney Sim Gill.
