OL,6,F"We are grateful to the survivor in
OL,7,Fthis case for her willingness to come
OL,8,Fforward, years after this attack took
OL,9,Fplace," Gill said in a statement on
OL,10,FWednesday night.
OL,12,F"We appreciate her patience as we
OL,13,Fworked to bring the defendant back to
OL,14,FSalt Lake County so that this trial
OL,15,Fcould take place and she could get
OL,16,Fjustice.
OL,18,F"It took courage and bravery to take
OL,19,Fthe stand and confront her attacker to
OL,20,Fhold him accountable."
