OL,6,FHow was Nicholas Rossi found?
OL,8,FUS authorities began searching for
OL,9,FRossi, whose legal name is Nicholas
OL,10,FAlahverdian, when he was identified
OL,11,Ffrom a decade-old rape kit in 2018,
OL,12,Ffollowing a push by Utah County to
OL,13,Fclear its rape kit backlog.
OL,15,FBy the time he was charged, he was
OL,16,Fbelieved to have already been in the
OL,17,FUK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
