OL,6,FIn December 2019, media and friends in
OL,7,FRhode Island began receiving calls
OL,8,Ffrom Rossi to say he was dying of
OL,9,Fcancer.
OL,11,FIn 2020, an online obituary claimed
OL,12,FRossi had died from late-stage non-
OL,13,FHodgkin lymphoma, seemingly written by
OL,14,Fhimself. State police and his former
OL,15,Ffoster family doubted this claim.
