OL,6,FA man calling himself Arthur Knight
OL,7,Fwas then admitted to hospital in
OL,8,FGlasgow in October 2021 with Covid-19.
OL,9,FHowever, staff noticed that his
OL,10,Ftattoos matched an Interpol notice and
OL,11,Falerted authorities.
OL,13,FAfter his arrest, he insisted that he
OL,14,Fwas not Nicholas Rossi, but an Irish
OL,15,Forphan. He spoke in a part-Irish and
OL,16,FEnglish accent, and said he had never
OL,17,Fvisited the US.
OL,19,FHowever, in 2022, Edinburgh Sheriff
OL,20,FCourt ruled this to be an alias and
OL,21,Fsaid he was in fact Nicholas Rossi.
