OL,6,FIn fact, GP records from the UK showed
OL,7,Fhe'd used a number of names - first
OL,8,FNicholas Brown, then Nicholas Knight
OL,9,FBrown, followed by Arthur Winston
OL,10,FKnight Brown, and then lastly omitting
OL,11,FBrown.
OL,13,FHe was extradited to the US in January
OL,14,F2024. In October of the same year, he
OL,15,Fadmitted that Arthur Knight was an
OL,16,Falias, and he was Nicholas Rossi.
